{"tid":2379527,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.14 沙田襲警案　督察宣誓不懂讀「謹」字　稱英國讀書中文「麻麻」","createTime":"2021-01-25T09:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T10:26:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2a2ebaf633cb15c5bdee068a51a037ad291f48","tid":2379527,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"去年 7 月沙田大遊行中，一名 26 歲電腦技術員被指以雨傘敲打督察雙手一下，遭控襲警罪。案件今（ 25 日）於沙田法院開審，報稱被襲的督察察葉浩明（譯音）同意現場片段拍不到事發經過，但強調在開拍前一秒發生。他又指被襲後感痛楚，但卻沒有前往醫院驗傷。葉浩明在宣誓時，曾一度不懂讀「謹此宣誓」的「謹」字，他解釋自己在英國讀書，故「讀同寫（中文）都麻麻」。<br />\n<br />\n案發時任機動部隊訓練小隊第 4 隊的督察霍建文供稱，當晚他與十多名同袍進入新城市廣場掃蕩，惟廣場內逾一百人聚集在欄杆旁，向警方投擲水樽、雨傘及鐵架等雜物，遂沿扶手電梯往上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-14-沙田襲警案-督察宣誓不懂讀-謹-字-稱英國讀書中文-麻麻/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-14-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%82%E8%AE%80-%E8%AC%B9-%E5%AD%97-%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%AE%80%E6%9B%B8%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-%E9%BA%BB%E9%BA%BB%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=f0de55b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-14-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%82%E8%AE%80-%E8%AC%B9-%E5%AD%97-%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%AE%80%E6%9B%B8%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-%E9%BA%BB%E9%BA%BB%2F&h=e8c5bb98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-14-沙田襲警案-督察宣誓不懂讀-謹-字-稱英國讀書中文-麻麻/</a>"},{"pid":"518db9cb20ea9701f9777cb4892e0d7a73fecae0","tid":2379527,"uid":298225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:40:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾你想點？？"},{"pid":"6faa4a4b5d4c8869370bade23a390c305c9c5cf6","tid":2379527,"uid":298225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"518db9cb20ea9701f9777cb4892e0d7a73fecae0","tid":2379527,"uid":298225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:40:07.000Z